- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper uses machine learning techniques to detect and localize pallets using data from a 2D laser rangefinder. This involves image processing and computer vision techniques.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses machine learning techniques to detect and localize pallets. This is a core area of machine learning research.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses AI techniques to enable AGVs to detect and track pallets. This falls under the domain of AI research.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper is about the automation of warehouse and shop-floor environments using AGVs. This falls under the domain of systems and control research.
